  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Living in Malta
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Official information for UK nationals moving to or living in Malta, including guidance on residency, passports and driving and the Withdrawal Agreement.</p>

  </div>
</div>

